## Requirements

- GLPI 10.x or 11.x
- PHP 7.4+ with the `curl` extension
- Network access to `api.rg-supervision.com` (HTTPS 443)

### Required rights on the GLPI API profile

```
Administration → Profiles → [API Profile] → Assistance → Ticket categories = Read
```

