## Installation

```sh
# Clone or download the repository
git clone https://github.com/your-repo/glpi-rgsupervision-sync.git rgsupervision

# Copy to the GLPI plugins folder
cp -r rgsupervision /var/www/glpi/plugins/

# Set permissions
chown -R www-data:www-data /var/www/glpi/plugins/rgsupervision/
```

Then in GLPI:

```
Setup → Plugins → RG Supervision Sync → Install → Enable
```

### Update (without reinstalling)

```sh
unzip -o plugin_rgsupervision_v1.0.0.zip -d /var/www/glpi/plugins/
```

