## Behavior when an RG alert closes

| GLPI ticket status | Action |
|---|---|
| New (1) | ✅ Automatic resolution |
| In progress (2), Pending (3), Unvalidated (4) | 📋 One-time private info task |
| Resolved (5) or Closed (6) | ⏭ Nothing |

