## GLPI 10+ constraints and solutions applied

| Issue | Solution |
|-------|----------|
| `$DB->query()` not allowed | `$DB->doQuery()` for DDL, `$DB->insert()` / `$DB->request()` for data |
| `Plugin::registerClass()` deprecated | Removed — GLPI 10+ handles autoloading of `inc/*.class.php` automatically |
| Assigning a group forces status to "In progress" | `$DB->update()` directly on `glpi_tickets` after creation to force "New" |
| `glpi_entities` has no `is_deleted` column | Filter removed from entity query |
| Method name conflicts with `CommonDBTM` | Static methods prefixed with `rg` (`rgUpdate`, `rgCreate`, etc.) |
| GLPI classes unavailable in CLI via `includes.php` | Initialization via the GLPI 10+ Symfony Kernel in `runcron.php` |

